{"tid":1832631,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"體育界人血饅頭，勿忘7.21","createTime":"2020-01-21T10:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T10:06:14.000Z","uid":31608,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"18e396367f180126d30ab537ae90465ac4c8f2d0","tid":1832631,"uid":31608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T10:06:14.000Z","msg":"琴晚睇到鏗鏘集，原來林奠條八婆就係一路幫班鄉黑搵套丁，賺大錢，唔怪之得咁撐佢。<br />\n<br />\n跟住睇到蘋果爆大獲，原來香港體育界都有班咁嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n話說原來跳繩界年年贏多獎，原來個亞繩盟無註冊。<br />\n<br />\n姐係點呀？求其搵到幾條友，拎住個Walkie ，就當封左路？就當比賽，我仲以為係頭D。<br />\n<br />\n【蘋果踢爆】港繩總夥無註冊組織辦亞錦賽 部份經費疑入大馬私人戶口 <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200120&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60490149\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200120%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60490149&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6uIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=40113f3e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200120%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60490149&h=27cc1448\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200120&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60490149</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n擺明亞繩同繩總就當運動員水魚，年年袋袋平安，當完水魚，之前教班運動仲扮慘，搞眾籌，話政府無資助，再掠多筆<br />\n<br />\n【蘋果踢爆】繩總4屆國際賽獲「分紅」逾百萬 自資參賽港將家長：聽都未聽過<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200120&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60490181\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200120%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60490181&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6uIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=660fe529\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200120%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D60490181&h=2788d1a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200120&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=60490181</a><br />\n<br />\n報出黎既年年40萬落袋，未計未報出黎<br />\n<br />\n眾籌錢同康文署錢，都係香港人錢黎架，屌你老母，呃9人扮無錢<br />\n<br />\n【蘋果踢爆】繩總世錦賽選拔準則「搬龍門」 前世界冠軍：我都難入選<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.co